        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Intro",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Choosing the right necklace for a V-neck outfit can completely elevate your look. Whether you prefer minimal elegance, bold statement pieces, or fine diamond jewellery, understanding <em>what necklace to wear with a V-neck</em> ensures your neckline appears elongated, balanced, and stylish.<br/> This guide also helps you understand what necklace to wear with what neckline and which necklace to wear with which neckline so you can style every outfit with confidence.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Understanding the V-Neckline",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Understanding the V-Neckline</h2><p>The V-neck is one of the most versatile and universally flattering necklines. It naturally draws the eyes downward, making your neck look longer and adding structure to your outfit.<br/> The right necklace should complement this shape instead of competing with it.</p>",
            "custom_id": "understanding",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BmD46M": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Best Necklaces  Paragaph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Best Necklaces to Wear With a V-Neck</h2>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_9CtBma": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Best_Necklace_To_Wear_With_V_neck_61b7b326-42d3-429d-bfad-6ccf9fd1d07e.png",
            "text": "<h3>1. Pendant Necklaces</h3><p>Pendant necklaces mirror the pointed structure of the V-neck, creating harmony and balance. They are ideal for both casual and formal looks.</p><h3>2. Drop Necklaces</h3><p>Drop necklaces enhance the elongating effect of the V-neck and work beautifully with deep or narrow V-shapes.</p><h3>3. Layered Necklaces</h3><p>A layered necklace set creates a soft cascading effect that complements shallow V-necks. Keep the layers delicate for a refined look.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "column",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "classic-lily-cut-diamond-pendant-necklace",
